{"tid":626593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法幻象2000戰機誤投炸彈，命中本土工廠","createTime":"2018-04-12T08:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T10:27:04.000Z","uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e3b70a999fa03a8930553b047a4c65989307ee","tid":626593,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:51:40.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕法國在當地時間10日驚傳一起罕見的意外，一架幻象2000戰機在飛經盧瓦雷省（Loiret）時，誤投一枚炸彈，這炸彈命中一家汽車零件工廠，造成2名員工受傷，所幸這枚炸彈是訓練用的空包彈不會引爆，否則後果不堪設想。<br />\n綜合法國媒體報導，法國盧瓦雷省在當地時間10日下午3點30分（台灣時間10日晚上9點30分），驚傳遭到「空襲」，一枚炸彈從天而降，命中當地一家汽車零件工廠，當場造成2名員工受傷，廠房內150名員工驚慌逃竄，得知有爆裂物後，消防人員急赴現場戒備，發現這枚炸彈沒有引爆風險後才解除封鎖。<br />\n目擊者指出，聽見戰機呼嘯而過後，就突然聽到一聲巨響，隨後消防單位立刻要所有人離開。<br />\n事後法國空軍出面坦承，一架訓練返航的幻象2000戰機飛經該區域時一枚訓練用空包彈脫落，誤擊工廠；空軍發言人指出，幻象2000搭載著空包彈，準備在靶場模擬空襲，但在飛行途中出現意外，發言人表示：「這是一起非常特殊與罕見的意外」詳細事故發生原因，軍方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2392138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2392138&d=nFNULF6bYlw0oEjJ%2BVHHJWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=458865f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2392138&h=729b853c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2392138</a></span>"},{"pid":"2e2babc5671c35245270d8a4ed106a9c13d62be4","tid":626593,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49f3e5b3fe9324432cb0090363de137ddcb0bcd9","tid":626593,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"打仗果陣咁搞法就死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一野炸爆友軍基地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55909b15e2cf29fcb33725171a65f0277ab79b63","tid":626593,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:30:16.000Z","msg":"你班歐豬和平得太耐"},{"pid":"a16c03616a41a0c6b001c5e26a6d5fb875367ed0","tid":626593,"uid":48817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"法軍一向垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636d7e54d4536f5b36001e4ebc746953e80a915a","tid":626593,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a16c03616a41a0c6b001c5e26a6d5fb875367ed0","tid":626593,"uid":48817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"法軍一向垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"二戰同意大利同級，專做豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebb95df3ff9a798457bee2332564106d42f499f","tid":626593,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16c03616a41a0c6b001c5e26a6d5fb875367ed0","tid":626593,"uid":48817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"法軍一向垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"有錢請班顧傭兵打鳩你 吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}